text: Jurques is a former commune. It is in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2017, it was merged into the new commune of Dialan sur Chaîne.Arrêté préfectoral 26 September 2016 ==Population== ==Related pages== *Communes of the Calvados department ==References== == Other websites == *INSEE Category:Former communes in Calvados
